Our answers are the same
for the seven questions. Looks like we'll make it this time.

23
00:02:11,980 --> 00:02:13,240
Hurry up. Question eight. Question eight.

24
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:14,900
Question eight. Still C.

25
00:02:14,900 --> 00:02:16,499
C?

26
